 observed a violation of hydrodynamical mass ordering between proton\nand $\\phi$-meson $v_{2}$ further supporting that $\\phi$-mesons are negligibly\naffected by the collective radial flow in the hadronic phase due to the small\nin-medium hadronic interaction cross sections.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 12 Feb 2017 16:53:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-20"}
