 to\nde-stabilize the binary in both SPH and grid simulations, but the effect is\nmore pronounced in the grid code.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 12 Feb 2017 19:27:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-05"}
