garithmic slope of the respective\nfree-stream or centerline velocity. The log-law parameters of the exterior\nlogarithmic region in channels and pipes are shown to depend monotonically on\nthe pressure gradient.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Feb 2017 07:47:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Feb 2017 15:02:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-20"}
